{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"fields":{"description":"## Reproduction Steps\n1. Push any change for review to Gerrit after the ~2026-07-04T01:38Z auto-deploy of main@151c2b69 onto box i-00880b2c7f13527c5.\n2. Observe the review bot posts NO LLM-Review vote.\n\n## Expected vs Actual\n- **Expected**: rebar review bot casts LLM-Review on every open change.\n- **Actual**: NO LLM-Review on changes 256+ (system-wide; all agents). Container serves /health 200 but every review fails internally with `Error: cannot list '/tmp/reviewbot-<x>/.tickets-tracker'`.\n\n## Root cause (PROVEN)\nproduce_code_review_verdict (src/rebar/llm/workflow/gate_dispatch.py) reused the pre-snapshot runner after gate_source.apply_handle re-rooted cfg onto the materialized ticket-store clone. get_runner(cfg, override=) returns the override verbatim and PydanticAIRunner.run reads its OWN baked-in self._config -> the agent's rebar tools ran against the bare clone (tickets_path None -> repo_path) -> missing .tickets-tracker -> review aborts, no vote. Introduced by e7a96025a.\n\n## Fix\nChange 264: rebuild runner_sel from the re-rooted cfg after apply_handle. RED->GREEN regression test with mutation-check teeth.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [x] Root cause pinned to the exact commit + code path (e7a96025a; gate_dispatch.py runner reuse)\n- [x] Fix lands on main; review bot resumes casting LLM-Review on new changes (verified: change 265 got LLM-Review+1 post-deploy)\n- [x] Regression test that is RED before the fix and GREEN after (tests/unit/test_code_review_gate_session.py::test_code_review_gate_runner_is_rebuilt_from_rerooted_ticket_store)\n\n## Follow-up (spun out, not part of this fix)\n- Functional readiness probe so ADR-0026 auto-rollback catches review-path failures -> task smoky-biome-queue (discovered_from this bug). The /health-only gate is a pre-existing defense-in-depth gap, not this regression."}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1783140485588830001,"uuid":"1ef82edd-d6be-47bb-9259-1a32b5b5b634"}